[ ] build VTODO integration ~ !1 #019f5847-e4ef-75f2-a736-831b6a828f63
    >[ ] learn to import VTODO $Action-mirror VTODO swap: action_to_vevent -> action_to_vtodo; Action.id is the VTODO UID and vdir filename, with no sidecar identity map. Map STATUS (blocked -> NEEDS-ACTION plus X-CLEARHEAD-STATUS:blocked), title, description, dates, priority, contexts, and completion. VTODO with RRULE is always a Plan; VTODO without RRULE is an Action projection.$ #019f5848-c3bf-7062-a94a-3abe216ea948
    >[ ] add fields to the sync store ~ $Genericize reconcile() to reconcile<T: PartialEq + Clone> and run it independently for state, title, description, and due_date. Each merge base lives in the one configured-plans-vdir projection store, never Action/ActionMeta. One field conflict must not block the others.$ #019f5848-c3bf-7062-a94a-3adcba9847ba
        >>[ ] state #019f5848-c3bf-7062-a94a-3afc680d10bc
        >>[ ] due date #019f5848-c3bf-7062-a94a-3b1aef80a19a
